{"tid":2450922,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Would you rather live in peace as Mr. Nobody...","createTime":"2021-03-17T18:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T22:00:17.000Z","uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d1e9d1e003193d51c5051f17f20fe542dd9322","tid":2450922,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:12:28.000Z","msg":"die ripe, old and smellin' slightly of urine? Or go down for all times in a blaze of glory, smellin' near like posies, 'thout seein' your thirtieth'?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經係我捱夜嘅第五日 為trans科繼續搏命 彷彿之中回到dse時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩年前因為貪婪同愚蠢做出一個錯誤決定 而家要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲各位中學雞揀major之前睇清楚<br />\n唔好相信咩雙學位雙主修環球金融資訊人脈經濟乜乜柒柒<br />\n呢啲buzzword永冇兌現之日 就算係真對我來講都一文不值<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚自己想要錢途定理想<br />\nQuiet life, or blaze of glory<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca7763fb7ae915792b7597a421508bddbe3e7e1","tid":2450922,"uid":300918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:16:44.000Z","msg":"連登啲升學po年中呃幾多中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d7e6d9986bf5086f202fdf3f370b2688dc00ca","tid":2450922,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca7763fb7ae915792b7597a421508bddbe3e7e1","tid":2450922,"uid":300918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:16:44.000Z","msg":"連登啲升學po年中呃幾多中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T22:00:17.000Z","msg":"係咁㗎啦 <br />\n希望中學雞聽多啲唔同嘅意見<br />\n理想同平庸 總有一樣啱<br />\n但係事實係大部份連登仔腦筍都未生埋<br />\n所以呢啲嘢都係要靠自己諗 同埋一定要快<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}